{"tid":2245583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台辣招限陸資 淘寶離場","createTime":"2020-10-16T10:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T11:13:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"818096c7531e3c123960786f73faa6ccfc1eef37","tid":2245583,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201016/4S6KIJIEPJGIJKHDMOBI2F7FRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201016%2F4S6KIJIEPJGIJKHDMOBI2F7FRQ%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=27702f04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201016%2F4S6KIJIEPJGIJKHDMOBI2F7FRQ%2F&h=a5aa0af1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201016/4S6KIJIEPJGIJKHDMOBI2F7FRQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台辣招限陸資 淘寶離場<br />\n<br />\n大陸網購平台龍頭淘寶去年進軍台灣，才不足一年時間便黯然退出台灣市場。淘寶台灣昨日發表聲明，宣佈於今年12月31日，正式停止在台灣的營運，昨日已停止落單，公司75名職員將被遣散，衝擊數十萬當地賣家的飯碗，這亦是繼愛奇藝後，第二個結束台灣業務的陸資疑慮網絡服務公司。阿里巴巴發言人表示，尊重在台營運公司的決定，阿里巴巴集團在台業務營運一切如常。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陸或終止ECFA報復<br />\n<br />\n在台負責營運「淘寶台灣」的英商克雷達昨發聲明，...........................。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qVloPa52O2LMIcaZ6TKhRXIGTdQ=/1026x995/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BJYGLM5QZJHGLCXULXRK7IWAMU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqVloPa52O2LMIcaZ6TKhRXIGTdQ%3D%2F1026x995%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBJYGLM5QZJHGLCXULXRK7IWAMU.gif&h=62859fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■淘寶台灣正協助賣方盡速履行已成立的交易定單。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅營運357天<br />\n<br />\n今年8月，為因應港區國安法通過，台灣經濟部出辣招限制陸資赴台，修正「大陸地區人民來台投資許可辦法」，不久後投審會公告，認定「淘寶台灣」是陸資。早於淘寶台灣成立之際，台灣官方已接到舉報指其為陸資，阿里巴巴透過新加坡子公司持克雷達股權雖然不到三成，未超陸資持股..............................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被揭為「陸資」<br />\n<br />\n這場網購平台風波，起因是淘寶台灣初以「英商」身份，而非「陸資」身份登台，但經查實質認定為「陸資」，...............................<br />\n<br />\n行政院發言人丁怡銘今天稱，行政院長蘇貞昌自上任以來，一直嚴格審查陸.......................<br />\n<br />\n.....................................，修補漏洞，防範陸資透過外資、港資名義偷渡來台，介入公司經營權，甚至進行經濟滲透。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"cb5384d795042572f0b2c16238913370573e606e","tid":2245583,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dec034cbb812b1b4199e03b48fd0ca2727520a","tid":2245583,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"冇寫&ldquo;中國台灣&rdquo; 大膽"}]}